COWORKING IN ETOBICOKE

Premium Flexible Office Space in a Prime Location in Etobicoke

We offer flexible month-to-month memberships that can be adjusted as your needs change.

Conveniently located in the Dundas Kipling Centre, just steps from the Kipling TTC Station and GO Station terminal.

State-of-the-art amenities and professional meeting rooms.

Secure, lockable offices with 24/7 membership access and free parking.

Customizable office spaces with cleaning and concierge-style service.
